        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google&#8217;s Pinpoint is the free research tool you should know about</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      This article is republished with permission from Wonder Tools, a newsletter that helps you discover the most useful sites and apps.
Google’s Pinpoint is now open to everyone. It’s a surprisingly powerful free tool for making sense of giant piles of digital stuff.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/06/13/googles-pinpoint-is-the-free-research-tool-you-should-know-about/"  >(Jeremy Caplan, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
