    <h3 itemprop="headline">Disaster drills helped prevent more deaths when powerful quake hit the southern Philippines</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Philippine officials say that years of disaster-preparedness drills helped prevent a larger casualty toll when one of the strongest earthquakes in 50 years struck the south.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/06/12/disaster-drills-helped-prevent-more-deaths-when-powerful-quake-hit-the-southern-philippines/"  >(Jim Gomez, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
