    <h3 itemprop="headline">Lotus Microsystems targets AI power efficiency with vStrata platform</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Lotus Microsystems has introduced vStrata, a new power-delivery architecture aimed at improving data-center power efficiency, which is a pressing concern even in non-AI environments.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/06/09/ai-power-efficiency-the-target-of-lotus-microsystems-energy-advances/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
